text: Mattias Guter (born July 23, 1988) is a Swedish professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Djurgårdens IF of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Guter made his Elitserien debut playing with Djurgårdens IF during the 2007–08 Elitserien season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Almtuna IS players Category:Djurgårdens IF Hockey players Category:Karlskrona HK players Category:Leksands IF players Category:Luleå HF players Category:IK Oskarshamn players Category:Swedish ice hockey right wingers Category:Timrå IK players Category:HC Vita Hästen players
